rmacons braskem was founded on january  9 and is headquartered in sao paulo brazil valuation enterprise value to ebitda  enterprise value to sales  efficiency receivables turnover  total asset turnover  liquidity current ratio  quick ratio  cash ratio  profitability gross margin  operating margin  pretax margin  net margin  return on assets  return on equity  return on total capital  return on invested capital  capital structure total debt to total equity 9 total debt to total capital 9 total debt to total assets  longterm debt to equity 9 longterm debt to total capital  officers and executives name age officer since title mr newton sérgio de souza   chairman mr fernando musa   chief executive officer mr pedro van langendonck de freitas   chief financial officer  headinvestor relations mr marcelo arantes de carvalho   directorpeople organization  it mr marcelo lyra do amaral   headinstitutional relations insider actions – purchase – sale  – number of transactions  except as otherwise noted the content of this page is licensed under the creative commons attribution  license and code samples are licensed under the apache  license for details see our site policies java is a registered trademark of oracle andor its affiliates last updated february   send feedback about this page documentation feedback freebase api deprecated product feedback cancel